      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REALITY SECRET (5) goes very well at the course with two wins and a placing from five starts. Comes off a (25.78) win last time, scoring by 5 lengths in a Restricted WIN over 460m at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. STEAL THE STAGE (8) is better than last start when sixth (24.25) in a Maiden FIN at Bendigo over 425m. Won at his only start from this draw. Better than last start and can bounce back. PAW XEROX (1) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at The Meadows following on from a second place finish (30.21) there the start prior. Has never been out of the placings from two starts out of this box. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. CARTMAN (2) scored with plenty to spare last time. Sure to run well again.",
